These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, sprite, hot-chocolate, coffee, fanta, juice
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indonesian, italian, nigerian, spanish, thai
 1. the thai is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the brazilian is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 3. the brazilian is not to the left of the french##8
 4. the french is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the spanish##8
 6. the person drinking 7up is not the french##6
 7. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
 9. the nigerian is somewhere between the thai and the french##7
10. the french is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
12. the spanish is on the right of the thai##1
13. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
14. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the nigerian and the brazilian##7
15. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the brazilian##1
16. the spanish is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
17. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
18. the person drinking juice is the indonesian##1
19. the nigerian is on the left or right of the thai##3
20. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the spanish##6
21. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
22. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage           | fanta | sprite | juice | cola  | coffee  | hot-chocolate | 7up    |
| Nationality   | french   | brazilian   | indonesian   | italian | nigerian | thai        | spanish |

