.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, camping, dancing, drawing, filmmaking, photography, puzzles
7 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, snooker, backgammon, bridge, scrabble
 1. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing bridge is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
 3. the person playing whist is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 4. the person playing bridge is between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing whist is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
14. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
15. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | drawing | dancing    | camping | filmmaking | board-games | photography |
| Game     | chess     | bridge   | billiard | backgammon | snooker       | whist        | scrabble      |

