.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blue, chestnut, orange, blood-red, azure, aquamarine
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, golf, lacrosse, parkour, rugby, snowboarding
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who likes blue##8
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 8. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
11. the person who likes blood-red is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is golf##2
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person who likes fuchsia##6
14. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
