7 different pets are kept: cat, dog, ferret, frog, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 9. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
11. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
13. the owner of the lizard is the person drinking milk##1
14. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
15. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
16. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
17. the owner of the goldfish is not the person drinking cola##6
18. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
19. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |    6     |   7    |
